additional_info:
If you'd like to use this elsewhere, the CSS is

@-moz-document domain(ark.fandom.com) {
.global-navigation {
display: none;
}
#mixed-content-footer {
display: none;
}
.wds-global-footer {
display:none;
}
#WikiaBar {
display: none;
}
.page__right-rail {
display: none;
}
}

You can modify the domain specification to just fandom.com to remove this clutter on all wikis if you like as well.

